  <scopecontent id="aspace_3b1ce7beabbfbc4dea71a33ba351b10a">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Scrapbooks, banquet programs from the sorority, and a history. Also newsletters, January and September 1998; 1921 and 1936 volumes of "Songs of Alpha Phi"; biographical information about members; guestbook; obituaries of members; and other miscellany relating to the sorority. Also group portraits, 1950 and 1951; composite photographs, 1956 and 1957; and groups at parties,1950s.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_4cf90eb1159a3911cadb62d554f7946b">
    <head>Preferred Citation</head>
<p>Alpha Phi, Delta chapter Records, #37-4-2132.  Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <bioghist id="aspace_e7f15d6ea4741bd31e176c1d60650cba">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>The Delta chapter of Alpha Phi was founded at Cornell University in 1889.</p>  </bioghist>
